0 You can leave your stuff in this Warehouse. The top row shows your items. The bottom row reflects all the items you keep in the Warehouse. To take or leave an item, select an item using the central button, then choose the number of items using left, right, up and down buttons. Then confirm changes in the menu. You are to pay a small daily fee for every item kept in the Warehouse. You don't lose things from the Warehouse in case you are defeated in a battle.
1 - Number "7" shows the numberof items.
2 - Number "12" shows the number of selected items.
3 - An item's race is shown in its bottom left corner.
4 - Number "142" is the daily fee.  
5 - Number "3" is the item's level.
6 - The items you can put on are marked with a green tick. You can use only those items that belong to friendly races. If you want to use an item, its level must not exceed yours.
7 - The items that you cannot put on are marked with a red cross. However, you can take them away with you, sell or exchange them.
